Package com.goldeninnovations.smp

Interface Summary
MessageFilter Allows incoming email messages to be filtered by the recipient's email address.
MessageProcessor Implement this interface to receive incoming email messages for processing.
MessageSpool Implement this interface to provide a custom spooling implementation.
SMPServerMBean MBean Interface describing the management options for the SMPServer
 

Class Summary
EmailAddress Represents a single email address.
EmailMessage Represents an incoming Email Message.
MessagePart Represents a single message part of a multipart message.
SMPServer Simple Message Processor Server
